data.description: Beautiful and quiet picture perfect home in east Beatrice! This home has two cozy living spaces on the main floor, beautiful and open all seasons room, formal and eat-in dining spaces, 4 spacious bedrooms all on the same floor including master suite, updated baths, finished basement family room, oversized garage and much more. The exterior contains a large well maintained yard, mature trees, and additional storage shed.  Here are some updates we made while we were here:  Updated Kitchen and Dining Flooring Updated Kitchen Cabinets, and Appliances Updated Kitchen and Dining Light Fixtures Added a Ceiling Fan to the Living Room Updated all outlets and switches on main floor to white and paddle switches. Added a Privacy fence to the North and South sides of the back yard.  Come fall in love with this neighborhood and enjoy joining this great community!
